    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example of the legendary S54-powered icon. The 3.2L inline-six delivers linear power through individual throttle bodies, with the dual-VANOS system recently overhauled for optimal cam timing. Power is sent via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a variable M-differential. The chassis is structurally flawless, featuring proactive subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings to maintain factory-spec torsional rigidity. Finished in Alpine White over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the exterior retains its original paint depth with no oxidation or panel misalignment. Mechanically sound and aesthetically untouched, this is a turnkey investment for the discerning driver.",
